      "startTime": 2.9666665714
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "会場は盛り上がっているわね。まだ開演前なのに\nお客さんの歓声がここまで聞こえてくるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.30937846,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.657845974
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "それだけ、私達とトリエルの対戦が\n注目されているのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.8629813194,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.8911793073
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "活動を再開してから、トリエルは絶好調……\nスリクスにも勝って、多分今がトリエル史上最強……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.924512736,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.7245126407
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "そのトリエルが、因縁の相手でBIG4の\nサニピと戦う……これは日本中が注目するのも当然……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.8578460693,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.0666656494
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "日本中が注目……\nそう言われたら、さらに緊張してきたよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.6376726404,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.7312233925
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "……さくら？　さっきからずっと黙り込んでるけど\nもしかして、何か心配事があるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.2666656494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.2115856488
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "体調のことを気にしているのなら\n何があっても私達がさくらちゃんを支えるから安心して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.9115857441,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.6333340962
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、そばに居るから\n何も不安に感じることなんてないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.7333340962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.8557595252
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃんは私達を信じて……\n心を繋いで……思い切り歌って踊ればいい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.2890929538,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.2224261919
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 77.5557596205
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "うん……。みんな、ありがとう\nでも、私が緊張してるのは不安だからじゃないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.3294432629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.1962805747
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "この緊張は、ワクワクしてるからなんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.1962805747,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "VENUSグランプリでトリエルと競い合えることが\n嬉しくて、楽しみで、ワクワクしてるんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.4256832562,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.6174583593
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "その気持ち、分かる……\n私も、瑠依さんとの勝負にワクワクしてる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.8838719835,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.1174583593
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "私もワクワクしてるわ\nこれもさくらちゃんの影響かしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.5121428778,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.2507916926
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃんと出会ってなかったら、こんな大舞台で\n楽しもうなんて、きっと考えられなかった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.7999997456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.5783200103
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "いつも間近で、ステージを楽しむさくらを見てきたから\n私達も思い切り楽しめるようになったのかもね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.4999997456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.0803378263
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "私だけが支えられてる訳じゃない……\n私達は五つのピース、みんながみんなを支えてる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.823440528,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.6011539935
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "五人で支え合って、影響を与え合ってきたから\n私達はここまで来られたんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.0666664123,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 142.9699745018
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "そうよ。私達がさくらちゃんを支えるから\nさくらちゃんの笑顔で私達を支えてね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.5033079305,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.8033078352
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_sun-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 151.6699745971
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.0999997456
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　支え合って、五つのピースを一つに重ねて……\n想いを繋げて、最高のステージにしよう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.6278505548,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 162.1507679461
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "さあ繋げよう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.1507679461,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 164.1841012794
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_03-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "みんなの想いを",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
